verbose_text: Besides, we were also attracted by another interesting phenomenon : the TH modification on the liposome appeared to be conducive to the immune stimulating effect of alphaGC, which was embodied as higher accumulation of liposomes in spleen, enhanced IFN-gamma secretion, and promoted alphaGC presentation.
